Hungary Court Strikes Down Law on Firing of Civil Servants

-- B y   Z o l t a n   S i m o n
-- 
2011-02-15T14:50:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-15/hungary-court-strikes-down-law-on-firing-of-civil-servants.html
Hungary’s Constitutional Court
struck down parts of a law passed last year that opened the way
for the firing of civil servants without justification,
according to a  ruling  posted on the court’s  website  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zoltan Simon in Budapest at 
 zsimon@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Willy Morris at 
 wmorris@bloomberg.net  